{"tid":1963711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"顯徑邨中電地盤壓地機搶火，工人臉燒傷送院","createTime":"2020-04-08T10:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T12:31:22.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ccad8b98af65a41ec555e3ebb2c23d1682af8398","tid":1963711,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"早上約10時半，一名62歲姓羅男工人於沙田顯徑邨商場對開行人路工作期間，其操作的壓地機發生搶火，羅男走避不及臉部被燒傷，工友見狀立即用水將火撲熄及報警，救護員到場，傷者清醒送院治理。<br />\n現場消息指出，涉事工地為中電鋪設電纜的地盤，警方經調查後，相信傷者當時加水到一個懷疑曾盛載易燃液體的水樽引起火花，導致搶火。事件沒有可疑，列工業意外交由勞工處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中電發言人回覆稱，該承辦商工人當時正進行壕坑工程，在操作手提切割工具期間，懷疑工具發生故障產生火花，導致工人左前臂受傷，事故未有影響電力供應，但中電亦已即時暫停工程，並要求承辦商調查事故原因。"},{"pid":"f33d8a763ca974336041a544dd977acd5b6e8a1e","tid":1963711,"uid":313514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4f613f16b8f45531fc937ea0fb61496ec5c7bc1","tid":1963711,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"咁佢同事倒野落去搞到仲大火做咩唔講"},{"pid":"ecbe4f2c937e51cb201ea5232ecb2d2b4acd09a6","tid":1963711,"uid":31303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f33d8a763ca974336041a544dd977acd5b6e8a1e","tid":1963711,"uid":313514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"片？"},{"pid":"a252e30e84733d3bb3e100be2f0b8d0d4ced7dcc","tid":1963711,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3831521623555540/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F3831521623555540%2F&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=5e8d1f37\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3831521623555540/</a><br />\n<br />\n水你老母"},{"pid":"34cfe795e82918366b3939dea7338d7de213bc1f","ti